# PLAYER::SET_PLAYER_HAS_RESERVE_PARACHUTE

## Summary
Allows script to control the tint index of the parachute pack

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This function gives the player a reserve parachute.
